settings.title: Free Delivery
settings.text: On all UK Mainland orders above £250. The shipping cost will be automatically deducted once your order exceeds £250 net.

settings.title: Customs and duties
settings.text:
Customers with shipping addresses out of Great Britain are
solely responsible for all duties and import taxes.

These charges are not included in the cost of shipping or
handling of your order.

Customs, duties, and taxes vary widely from country to
country; please check with your local customs agency for details on estimated
costs.

Customs, duty, and taxes are non-refundable so if you
refuse a shipment because of unexpected import fees, the cost of the original
shipping, any brokerage/customs/duty/taxes, and any return shipping charges
will not be refunded.

settings.title: Worldwide Shipping
settings.text:
We ship to over 100 countries around the world.

All orders paid by 13:00 GMT will be shipped same day. The cost will be calculated automatically.

settings.title: UK Next Day Delivery
settings.text: All orders paid by 13:00 GMT pm will be dispatched same day for the Next Day Delivery.

settings.title: Order Tracking
settings.text:
Once the order is paid and ready for shipment, shipment tracking number will be emailed in the shipping update email.

Please contact us on +44(0)1865 241236 if you need any further information regarding shipment tracking details.

settings.title: Dispatch Time
settings.text:
All orders paid by 1pm GMT will be dispatched the same day.

Orders placed after 1pm will be dispatched next day.

Orders placed on Friday after 1 pm GMT will be dispatched on Monday.

settings.title: Can you deliver to a different address than my billing address?
settings.text: Yes we can. As long as the right address is provided in the shipping address column, that is the address that the package will be shipped to.

settings.title: My order hasn't arrived, could you tell me where it is?
settings.text:
If your order has not arrived by the estimated delivery date, we're here to help.

Before getting in contact with us, have you tried tracking your order on-line? The tracking link for the couriers we use are as following:

Your order tracking number and link is emailed after the order is placed and the dispatched from our warehouse.

settings.title: Shipping Destinations
settings.text:
Catwalk Wholesale ships Worldwide.

If there are no shipping quotes available for your country please contact us so that we can add it.

settings.title: Delivery Time
settings.text:
The estimated delivery times are as follows:

UK: 99.99% of our packages arrive the next working day

US: 99.99% of our packages arrive the next working day

Worldwide: Delivery within 2 – 4 working days

Europe: 1-3 working days

Rest of the World: 2-6 Working Days

settings.title: What if I am not home when my parcel is delivered?
settings.text:
The delivery company might in some cases leave it with a neighbour but in most cases a signature is needed. If that is the case, then they will attempt to delivery again the next day.

They usually do leave a note to say that they tried to deliver.
